  "rationale": "<p>Distribute: (n \u2212 4)(6n\u00b2 \u2212 5) = n(6n\u00b2 \u2212 5) \u2212 4(6n\u00b2 \u2212 5) = 6n\u00b3 \u2212 5n \u2212 24n\u00b2 + 20. Reordering: 6n\u00b3 \u2212 24n\u00b2 \u2212 5n + 20. Among the choices, (c) is 6n\u00b3 \u2212 5n \u2212 24n\u00b2 + 20, which is equivalent. Choice (c) is correct.</p>",
